{
  "stem": "8423.3",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they say, fold your clothes very neatly and put it on the benches along the wall, so when after you have a shower, you come back and get it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And your shoes under the bench.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they're giving us all these directions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Line up--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now it's all German, all German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now were all German soldiers there, with their rifles, with their sticks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they're hitting anybody who is not doing what they're supposed to do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or if you're frozen, and you kind of don't know how to move to get undressed or whatever, they woke you up with the stick.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They gave you, you know-- they hit you, to kind of bring you back to yourself.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So, you know, you couldn't block out if you wanted to.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it was a huge white room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It looked like the whole thing was marble, all white, white, white marble benches, white marble floors.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they made us go single file here to have our hair cut.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I saw them shaving these people, I started to cry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think that's the first I cried.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my sister said to me, OK, I'll go first.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there were my sister's gorgeous blonde hair on the floor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they make her raise her arms so they can do her underarms and the pubic hair, all done by a man.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they're telling the man, schnell, schnell, schnell.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Thank you very much.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
